\pard\plain \s2\f0\fs24\sb240\sl240\ql But tonight, tonight is different. \par
\pard\plain \s2\f0\fs24\sb240\sl240\ql He notices someone is following him, a masked man. He increases his pace, and in no time, he starts running, only to see another masked man standing at the end of the street. \par
