\pard\plain \s2\f0\fs24\sb240\sl240\ql Mathew tries to push Sudheer(in the mask) to escape, but\par
\pard\plain \s2\f0\fs24\sb240\sl240\ql \b --BAM!!\par
\pard\plain \s2\f0\fs24\sb240\sl240\ql He is punched hard on his gut. He falls down on his knees, struggling in pain.\par
\pard\plain \s2\f0\fs24\sb240\sl240\ql Purushottam grabs his head and shows him the picture of a girl.\par
