\pard\plain \s5\f0\fs24\sb0\sl240\li1389\ri2083\ql It was 12 years ago, I tried to confess, they did not let me. I was in an asylum for the next 4 years. I have a wife now, and two daughters, they are 4 and 5 years old. I\u8217?m a changed person now.\par
